=== Proper noun ===
'''Apple'''

#('''the Apple''') A [[nickname]] for [[New York City]] (''usually'' '''the Big Apple''').
#('''&reg;''') A [[multimedia]] [[corporation]] ([[w:Apple Corps|Apple Corps]]) and [[record]] [[company]] ([[w:Apple Records|Apple Records]]) founded by the [[w:Beatles|Beatles]].
#('''&reg;''') Name of the [[company]], [[w:Apple Computer|Apple Computer]], that produces computers and other [[digital]] devices.
#('''&reg;''') A [[computer]] produced by the company Apple Computer.
# (''rare'') a [[female]] [[given name]].

